FinOps Benchmark Report - European Enterprises 2024

AVERAGE CLOUD SPEND:
- Large enterprise (>5000 employees): EUR 4.2M/year
- Mid-market (500-5000): EUR 680K/year
- SMB (<500): EUR 85K/year

WASTE ANALYSIS:
- Average overprovisioning: 27%
- Unused reserved instances: 14%
- Orphaned resources: 8%
- Total waste: ~32% of cloud spend

COST OPTIMIZATION RESULTS:
- Companies with FinOps practice: 18% less waste
- Automated rightsizing: saves avg 22% on compute
- Reserved instance optimization: saves avg 35% vs on-demand

TOP COST DRIVERS:
1. Compute (48%)
2. Storage (22%)
3. Data transfer (15%)
4. Managed services (12%)
5. Support plans (3%)

Detailed data attached. Dashboard: cloudcfo.example/benchmark

Cloud CFO Network
